               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of a work by Murshid al-Dīn ʿAbd Allāh ibn ʿAlī al-Shīftagī
                     al-Shīrāzī</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2010105554 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2008109073"
                     n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_525-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic </textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled extensive commentary by <persName key="person_f8054" role="aut"
                              >Murshid al-Dīn ʿAbd Allāh ibn ʿAlī al-Shīftagī al-Shīrāzī</persName>
                           on the famous Persian mas̲navī on Arabic vocabulary, the <title
                              key="work_211">Niṣāb al-ṣibyān</title> of <persName
                              xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_13150645168410622328" role="aut"
                              >Abū Naṣr Muḥammad Badr al-Dīn Farāhī</persName>. </p>
                        <p>The manuscript has another feature added by a later owner, who inserted
                           Arabic quotations on the top of every folio’s verso indicating the volume
                           was used for istikhārat or bibliomancy. </p>
                        <p>Dated colophon (f. 95v): completed Friday… 1001/1592-3. </p>
                        <p>Neat nastaʿlīq inclining toward scribal shikastah āmīz by the end.
                           Awkward naskh hand added by later owner. </p>
                        <p>Stamped foliation. </p>
                        <p>Damaged reddish brown leather binding, detached. </p>
                        <p>Folios partially bound; cropped, stains, minor wormhole damage, later
                           repairs; large sections torn at the end. </p>
                        <p>Condition fragile. </p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_f8054">Murshid al-Dīn ʿAbd
                           Allāh ibn ʿAlī al-Shīftagī al-Shīrāzī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_f8054">مرشد الدّين عبد الله ابن على
                           الشّيفتگى الشّيرازى</persName>
                     </author>
